t Elon Musk,=E2=80=99 Bartash said. =E2=80=98He=E2=80=99s Steve Jobs but mu=
ltiplied by an order of magnitude. I=E2=80=99m not a cultist, but it=E2=80=
=99s like biblical proportions when he talks about wanting to democratize s=
pace and going to Mars.=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D
