<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><strong>Programming note:</strong> <em>Money S=
tuff will be off tomorrow, back on Wednesday.</em></p>
<table class=3D"header" width=3D"100%" border=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" cellp=
adding=3D"0">
<tr>
<td class=3D"body-header-container" style=3D"border-collapse: collapse; mso=
-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt;">
<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">Oops</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The story is: Jane Street Group, the proprieta=
ry trading firm,=C2=A0found some clever and counterintuitive trading strate=
gy and made a lot of money doing it. Then some of the guys who did the trad=
e left Jane Street for Millennium Management, where Jane Street thinks they=
 are doing the same trade. Now Jane Street is making less money doing the t=
rade, and is unhappy about this. So it sued the guys, and Millennium, for t=
heft of trade secrets. We <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/35121691.265351/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGV=
zLzIwMjQtMDQtMTkvamFuZS1zdHJlZXQtcy1zZWNyZXQtc3RyYXRlZ3ktY29uY2VybnMtaW5kaW=
EtaGVhcmluZy1yZXZlYWxzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA0MjIyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09Z=
W1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDQyMiZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249=
bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBd24d8f46" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" it=
emscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decor=
ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">discussed the law=
suit last week</a>.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One obvious problem with Jane Street=E2=80=99s=
 approach is that, if you are an <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/35121691.265351/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2Fy=
dGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDQtMTcvamFuZS1zdHJlZXQtc2NvcmVzLTEwLTYtYmlsbGlvbi10cmFkaW5=
nLWhhdWwtYW1pZC1ncm93dGgtcHVzaD9jbXBpZD1CQkQwNDIyMjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbW=
VkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDA0MjImdXRtX2Nhb=
XBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBe7deba1e" itemprop=3D"Story=
Link" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; te=
xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">extraordi=
narily profitable</a> and somewhat secretive proprietary trading firm, and =
you file a public lawsuit saying =E2=80=9Csomeone stole our extraordinarily=
 profitable and secret proprietary trading strategy,=E2=80=9D people are go=
ing to be <em>very interested</em>. Everyone is going to try to figure out =
what the strategy is.=C2=A0Of course, if you are Jane Street, people are al=
ways trying to figure out what your strategies are, but filing the lawsuit =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0even if you redact=C2=A0all the details of the trading strat=
egy =E2=80=94=C2=A0is going to give them an extra incentive, and=C2=A0some =
clues.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">For instance <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/35121691.265351/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9=
uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDQtMTkvamFuZS1zdHJlZXQtcy1zZWNyZXQtc3RyYXRlZ3ktY2=
9uY2VybnMtaW5kaWEtaGVhcmluZy1yZXZlYWxzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA0MjIyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJ=
nV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDQyMiZ1=
dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cCd24d8f46" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
here is a hilarious clue</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The allegedly secret trading strategy over whi=
ch Jane Street Group is suing two former traders and Millennium Management =
involves options trading in India, lawyers inadvertently revealed at a cour=
t hearing.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Jane Street, which sued Millennium as well as =
former employees Douglas Schadewald and Daniel Spottiswood last week, had s=
ought to close the Friday hearing before US District Judge Paul Engelmayer =
in Manhattan. The judge denied that request but urged the parties to avoid =
mentioning any trade secrets. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At Friday=E2=80=99s hearing, a Jane Street law=
yer said the strategy was one of the firm=E2=80=99s most profitable and exp=
ressed fear that even identifying the country involved would lead to others=
 =E2=80=9Cpicking apart=E2=80=9D the details. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But lawyers for Millennium, Schadewald and Spo=
ttiswood identified the nation as India during their arguments, at multiple=
 points apologizing to the judge for doing so.=C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In theory I suppose that Millennium=C2=A0<em>a=
lso=C2=A0</em>has incentives to keep the trade secret: Supposedly Millenniu=
m is also making money with this trade, and it=E2=80=99s=C2=A0better for Mi=
llennium if the trade is known only to it and Jane Street than if it is kno=
wn to everyone. On the other hand, it is=C2=A0extremely funny<em>=C2=A0</em=
>for Millennium to be like =E2=80=9Coh the India trade? We thought everyone=
 knew about the India trade=E2=80=9D and further blow up Jane Street=E2=80=
=99s spot.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Everyone, I suppose, is playing a long game he=
re. The India options trade cannot be long for this world; really, as soon =
as Schadewald and=C2=A0Spottiswood left Jane Street for Millennium, its day=
s were numbered. Secret lucrative market anomalies cannot stay secret and l=
ucrative forever; the market for traders, and trading strategies, is=C2=A0<=
em>somewhat=C2=A0</em>efficient. Jane Street is not really suing to get its=
 India strategy back; that=E2=80=99s a lost cause. Jane Street is suing to =
scare its=C2=A0<em>other=C2=A0</em>employees, to deter them from taking=C2=
=A0<em>other=C2=A0</em>clever trades to competitors =E2=80=94=C2=A0and to s=
care those competitors, to deter them from=C2=A0<em>hiring=C2=A0</em>Jane S=
treet employees to replicate their Jane Street trades.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And Millennium is, among other things, playing=
 a game of counter-deterrence. One could take the message from the hearing,=
 =E2=80=9Cif you sue us for copying your secret trades, we will go tell eve=
ryone about them.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Otherwise, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/35121691.265351/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZ=
XdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDQtMTgvZXgtamFuZS1zdHJlZXQtdHJhZGVycy1kZW55LXN0ZWFs=
aW5nLXNlY3JldHMtZm9yLW1pbGxlbm5pdW0_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQyMjI0X01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXR=
tX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjQwNDIyJnV0bV=
9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB1ab56cd8" itemprop=3D"S=
toryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000=
; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">the d=
efense</a> seems to be roughly <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
ss.com/click/35121691.265351/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2=
FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDQtMTgvamFuZS1zdHJlZXQtd2FudHMtaXRzLXNlY3JldHMtYmFjaz9jb=
XBpZD1CQkQwNDIyMjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3=
c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDA0MjImdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4=
b8524a319a23cB66fc3696" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targ=
et=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bo=
rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;">what we discussed last week</a>: Whatever S=
chadewald and Spottiswood took with them from Jane Street was not its confi=
dential intellectual property but just general knowledge of  how to make mo=
ney trading options.=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/35121691.265351/aHR0cHM6Ly9hc3NldHMuYndieC5pby9kb2N1bWVudHMvdXNlcnM=
vaXFqV0hCRmRmeElVL3I3dUtST3ZobWVmOC92MA/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB40e7ce5f" =
itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"c=
olor: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; =
border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color:=
 #ccc;">Their lawyer wrote</a>=C2=A0that they =E2=80=9Chave not used any ev=
en arguable trading secret of Jane Street in their trading at Millennium,=
=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Care simply practicing their profession.=E2=80=9D <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35121691.265351/aHR0c=
HM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDQtMTkvamFuZS1zdHJl=
