 itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-de=
coration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #=
000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">the most cynic=
al things I have ever seen</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I write to bring your attention to potential m=
arket manipulation of the stock of Trump Media &amp; Technology Group Corp.=
 (=E2=80=9CTMTG=E2=80=9D), which operates the Truth Social platform and has=
 traded on the Nasdaq Stock Market under the ticker =E2=80=9CDJT=E2=80=9D s=
ince March 26, 2024.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As you know, =E2=80=9Cnaked=E2=80=9D short sel=
ling=E2=80=94selling shares of a stock without first borrowing the shares o=
f stock deemed difficult to locate=E2=80=94is generally illegal pursuant to=
 Securities and Exchange Commission (=E2=80=9CSEC=E2=80=9D) Regulation SHO.=
=C2=A0As of April 17, 2024, DJT appears on Nasdaq=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9CReg SH=
O threshold list,=E2=80=9D=C2=A0which is indicative of unlawful trading act=
ivity. This is particularly troubling given that =E2=80=9Cnaked=E2=80=9D sh=
ort selling often entails sophisticated market participants profiting at th=
e expense of retail investors.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Reports indicate that, as of April 3, 2024, DJ=
T was =E2=80=9Cby far=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9Cthe most expensive U.S. stock to sh=
ort,=E2=80=9D meaning that brokers have a significant financial incentive t=
o lend non-existent shares. Data made available to us indicate that just fo=
ur market participants have been responsible for over 60% of the extraordin=
ary volume of DJT shares traded: Citadel Securities, VIRTU Americas, G1 Exe=
cution Services, and Jane Street Capital.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In light of the foregoing, and Nasdaq=E2=80=99=
s obligation and commitment to protect the interests of retail investors,=
=C2=A0please advise what steps you can take to foster transparency and comp=
liance by ensuring market makers are adhering to Reg SHO, requiring brokers=
 to disclose their =E2=80=9CNet Short=E2=80=9D positions, and preventing th=
e lending of shares that do not exist.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That is a letter from Devin Nunes, the ex-poli=
tician and current chief executive officer of Trump Media, to the Nasdaq, t=
he exchange that lists Trump Media=E2=80=99s stock; the company <a href=3D"=
https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35121691.265351/aHR0cHM6Ly93d=
3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzE4NDk2MzUvMDAwMTE0MDM2MTI0MDIwNTc1=
LzAwMDExNDAzNjEtMjQtMDIwNTc1LWluZGV4Lmh0bQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB002a33f=
b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">publicized the letter</a> on Friday morning. The premise of th=
is letter is that =E2=80=9Csophisticated market participants=E2=80=9D are =
=E2=80=9Cprofiting at the expense of retail investors=E2=80=9D by creating =
new shares of Trump Media stock and selling it to them. Which might be true=
! Except the =E2=80=9Csophisticated market participants=E2=80=9D are Trump =
Media=E2=80=99s promoters, who took the company public by merging it with a=
 special purpose acquisition company (SPAC)=C2=A0and who will be allowed to=
 sell=C2=A0their personal stakes when their lockups expire in September. Tr=
ump Media is deeply unprofitable and has very little revenue, but trades at=
 a market value of almost $5 billion, because its ticker symbol is Donald T=
rump=E2=80=99s initials, because its retail investors love Donald Trump, an=
d because it is, as Nunes points out, basically impossible to short.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">What can Nunes do to talk up the stock price? =
It seems hard for him to argue that Trump Media is=C2=A0<em>undervalued</em=
>. In 2023, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/351216=
91.265351/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9kb2M9L0FyY2hpdmVzL2VkZ2FyL2RhdGEvM=
