scope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decorat=
ion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00000=
0; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">a Wall Street Journ=
al article about that</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Costco=C2=A0made buying a gold bar as simple a=
s tossing it in a shopping cart. Selling it is a lot more complicated.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Adam Xi, 33 years old, called five different d=
ealers to get a price he could accept for the gold bar he bought at Costco =
in October.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One dealer offered him $200 less than the $2,0=
00 he had paid. Taking such a loss would thwart his plan to rack up credit-=
card points buying the gold and quickly reselling it.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I mean? Yes? I tremble to think of the number =
of TikToks and subreddits there must be about buying gold at Costco for cre=
dit-card points.</p>
